  "text": "Remark 3.3. It is easy to see that a mixing point process Ψ has the ergodicity property assumed in Theorem 3.2. Our main example, the stationary determinantal point processes are mixing; see Theorem 7 in [CITATION_1] and also Theorem 12.2 in the appendix for more quantitative bounds.",
